    countries: "Uganda",
    future: "A vision and dental clinic for the Bwindi Community Hospital. We are working with several organizations and other Rotary clubs to outfit the new clinic with equipment. We also hope to provide a CT scanner for the hospital.",
    collab: "We would appreciate suggestions on where to find refurbished/affordable vision and dental equipment for this hospital caring for an underserved population. The CT scanner is obviously a big expense. The equipment needs to be serviceable locally.",
